Class PreferencesStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>

    Serializable, Cloneable, Map<String,Object>

    public class PreferencesStore
extends PreferencesMap
    PreferencesStore relating to PKI that can be used across Sessions. This class would contain all preferences pertaining to PKI based operations.
